-- CSU’s Michelbach Calls for Temporary Halt to Greek Aid Payments
-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 2012-05-28T10:33:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-28/csu-s-michelbach-calls-for-temporary-halt-to-greek-aid-payments.html
Europe should implement a temporary
stop to aid for Greece, said Hans Michelbach, ranking member in
the German parliament’s finance committee for Chancellor Angela Merkel’s caucus partner the  Christian Social Union .  Greek political developments leave in “serious doubt”
whether the country will fulfill promised austerity measures,
Michelbach said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
